'''蚯蚓糞'''，是[[蚯蚓|蚯蚓]]分解[[有機物|有機物]]的最終產物。<ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite web |url=http://southwoodsforestgardens.blogspot.com/2009/01/paper-on-invasive-european-worms.html |title=Paper on Invasive European Worms |accessdate=2009-02-22 |archive-date=2019-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191009124334/https://southwoodsforestgardens.blogspot.com/2009/01/paper-on-invasive-european-worms.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>這些排泄物已被證明含有較低水平的污染物和營養物質的飽和度高於有機物質在蛭石粉碎之前。<ref name="Effects of stocking density and feeding rate on vermicomposting of biosolids">{{cite journal | author1 = Ndegwa, P.M. | author2 = Thompson, S.A. | author3 = Das, K.C. | title = Effects of stocking density and feeding rate on vermicomposting of biosolids | journal = Bioresource Technology | volume = 71 | issue =  | pages = 5–12 | year = 1998 | pmid =  | doi = 10.1016/S0960-8524(99)00055-3 | url = http://www.earthworm.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/effect-of-stocking-density-feeding-rate-on-vermicomposting-of-biosolids.pdf | access-date = 2017-10-02 | archive-date = 2017-08-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170808071348/http://www.earthworm.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/effect-of-stocking-density-feeding-rate-on-vermicomposting-of-biosolids.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>

蚯蚓成分含有水溶性營養成分，營養豐富[[有機肥|有機肥]]和土壤調理劑。<ref>Coyne, Kelly and Erik Knutzen. ''The Urban Homestead: Your Guide to Self-Sufficient Living in the Heart of the City.'' Port Townsend: Process Self Reliance Series, 2008.</ref> 它用於農業和小規模可持續的有機農業。

蚯蚓糞也可用於污水處理。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Zularisam|first=A.W.|last2=Zahir|first2=Z. Siti|last3=Zakaria|first3=I.|last4=Syukri|first4=M.M.|last5=Anwar|first5=A.|last6=Sakinah|first6=M.|title=Production of Biofertilizer from Vermicomposting Processes of Municipal Sewage Sludge|url=http://scialert.net/fulltext/?doi=jas.2010.580.584&org=11|journal=Journal of Applied Sciences|volume=10|issue=7|pages=580–584|doi=10.3923/jas.2010.580.584|access-date=2017-10-02|archive-date=2019-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230215551/https://scialert.net/fulltext/?doi=jas.2010.580.584|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite journal|title = A comparative study of synchronous treatment of sewage and sludge by two vermifiltrations using an epigeic earthworm Eisenia fetida|journal = Journal of Hazardous Materials|date = 2011-01-30|issn = 1873-3336|pmid = 21041027|pages = 881–888|volume = 185|issue = 2–3|doi = 10.1016/j.jhazmat.2010.09.103|first = Meiyan|last = Xing|first2 = null|last2 = JianYang|first3 = Yayi|last3 = Wang|first4 = Jing|last4 = Liu|first5 = Fen|last5 = Yu}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Pilot studies for vermifiltration of 1000m3day of sewage wastewater|url = http://www.academia.edu/4202404/Pilot_studies_for_vermifiltration_of_1000m3day_of_sewage_wastewater|website = www.academia.edu|access-date = 2016-02-21|archive-date = 2021-04-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210428205245/https://www.academia.edu/4202404/Pilot_studies_for_vermifiltration_of_1000m3day_of_sewage_wastewater|dead-url = no}}</ref>

==性質==
蚯蚓已被證明是更豐富的許多營養成分比堆肥產生的其他堆肥方法。它還具有優於養分增加，但需要調整鎂和pH值。

== 原料 ==
雖然肉類廢物和[[乳製品|乳製品]]可能會腐敗，但是室外垃圾箱可以吸引[[害蟲|害蟲]]，蚯蚓不能堆肥的食物廢物很少。

=== 小型或家庭系統 ===
這種系統通常使用廚房和花園廢物，使用蚯蚓和其他微生物來消化有機廢物。<ref>{{cite journal |first=Piper |last=Selden |first2=Michael |last2=DuPonte |first3=Brent |last3=Sipes |first4=Kelly |last4=Dinges |url=http://www.ctahr.hawaii.edu/oc/freepubs/pdf/HG-45.pdf |title=Small-Scale Vermicomposting |format=PDF |journal=Home Garden |volume=45 |publisher=University of Hawai'i |date=August 2005 |accessdate=2012-10-03 |archive-date=2021-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502072007/https://www.ctahr.hawaii.edu/oc/freepubs/pdf/HG-45.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>
這包括：
*所有水果和蔬菜（不包括[[柑橘|柑橘]]和其他'''高酸'''食品）
*使用過咖啡粉
*使用過茶葉
*糧食如麵包，餅乾和穀物（包括發霉和過時）
*蛋殼（沖洗掉）
*葉和草屑（不噴灑[[農藥|農藥]]<ref>{{cite journal|last=Reinecke|first=SA|author2=Reinecke, AJ|title=The impact of organophosphate pesticides in orchards on earthworms in the Western Cape, South Africa.|journal=Ecotoxicology and Environmental Safety|date=February 2007|volume=66|issue=2|pages=244–51|pmid=16318873|url=http://www.aseanenvironment.info/Abstract/41014272.pdf|format=PDF|doi=10.1016/j.ecoenv.2005.10.006|author=|access-date=2017-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020040824/http://www.aseanenvironment.info/Abstract/41014272.pdf|archive-date=2013-10-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>)
*報紙（大多數在報紙上使用的油墨都沒有毒性）
*紙巾（未與清潔劑或化學品一起使用）

=== 大型或商業 ===
這種蚯蚓分散系統需要可靠的大量食物來源。
目前使用的系統有：<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.jgpress.com/BCArticles/2000/110051.html |title=Latest Developments In Mid-To-Large-Scale Vermicomposting |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2012-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120626062526/http://www.jgpress.com/BCArticles/2000/110051.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
