== 收穫 ==
[[File:Worm.bin.jpg|right]]
蚯蚓已經準備好收穫，當它含有少量到沒有殘留的食物或床上用品，有幾種方法從小型系統收穫。<ref>Appelhof, pp. 79-86</ref>這些時間和勞動力的數量有所不同，以及蚯蚓分子是否希望將盡可能多的蠕蟲保存在被收穫的堆肥中。

收集蚯蚓糞的方法通常用於小規模養殖，單層垃圾箱被認為是最簡單的方法。<ref>{{Cite web|title = Urban Worm Composting - Harvest Vermicompost|url = http://www.urbanwormcomposting.org/harvest-vermicompost/|website = www.urbanwormcomposting.org|access-date = 2016-02-21|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151025172041/http://www.urbanwormcomposting.org/harvest-vermicompost/|archivedate = 2015-10-25}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Harvesting - MMSB - Multi-Materials Stewardship Board|url = http://www.mmsb.nl.ca/composting/vermicomposting/harvesting/|website = MMSB - Multi-Materials Stewardship Board|access-date = 2016-02-21|language = en-US|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151028062058/http://www.mmsb.nl.ca/composting/vermicomposting/harvesting/|archivedate = 2015-10-28}}</ref>

== 屬性 ==
在其他[[堆肥|堆肥]]方法生產的[[堆肥|堆肥]]中，蚯蚓糞已被證明比[[營養|營養]]更豐富。<ref>{{cite web |last=Dickerson |first=George W. |url=http://www.cahe.nmsu.edu/pubs/_h/h-164.pdf |title=Vermicomposting: Guide H-164 |publisher=New Mexico State University |format=PDF |date=June 2001 |accessdate=2012-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090115215337/http://www.cahe.nmsu.edu/pubs/_h/h-164.pdf |archive-date=2009-01-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 它也優於具有添加營養素的商業植物培養基，但是[[鎂|鎂]]的水平需要調節，[[pH值|pH值]]也是如此。<ref>{{cite web |last=Sherman |first=Rhonda |url=http://www.bae.ncsu.edu/topic/vermicomposting/vermiculture/castings.html |title=Earthworm Castings as Plant Growth Media |publisher=Department of Biological and Agricultural Engineering at NCSU |accessdate=2012-10-03 |archive-date=2006-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060117155144/http://www.bae.ncsu.edu/topic/vermicomposting/vermiculture/castings.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

然而，在一項研究中，已經發現，自製後院蚯蚓生物質的微生物量，土壤微生物活性和[[黑麥草|黑麥草]]的種類比市政堆肥的產量更低，它富含微生物生物，轉化了已經存在的 土壤變成植物形式。<ref name=autogenerated2>{{cite journal|last=Lazcano|first=Cristina|author2=Gómez-Brandón, María|author3=Domínguez, Jorge|title=Comparison of the effectiveness of composting and vermicomposting for the biological stabilization of cattle manure|journal=Chemosphere|date=July 2008|volume=72|issue=7|pages=1013–1019|doi=10.1016/j.chemosphere.2008.04.016|url=http://webs.uvigo.es/jdguez/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/Comparison-of-the-effectiveness-of-composting-and-vermicomposting.pdf|format=PDF|pmid=18511100|access-date=2017-10-02|archive-date=2012-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121202025849/http://webs.uvigo.es/jdguez/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/Comparison-of-the-effectiveness-of-composting-and-vermicomposting.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

與其他堆肥不同，蠕蟲鑄件還含有[[黏液|黏液]]，其有助於防止營養物質與第一次澆水沖洗，並保持比平原土壤更好的水分。<ref>Nancarrow, Loren; Taylor, Janet Hogan (1998). [https://books.google.com/books?id=rmtZ91zbxLMC&printsec=frontcover&dq=The+Worm+Book&source=bl&ots=h7KFpfKigc&sig=r_L-YXzDAst_-lmjRkLuXcX3vqo&hl=en&sa=X&ei=DChsUNS2Oei40gHJvIH4CQ&ved=0CDEQuwUwAA#v=onepage&q&f=false ''The Worm Book: The Complete Guide to Gardening and Composting with Worms''] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rmtZ91zbxLMC&printsec=frontcover&dq=The+Worm+Book&source=bl&ots=h7KFpfKigc&sig=r_L-YXzDAst_-lmjRkLuXcX3vqo&hl=en&sa=X&ei=DChsUNS2Oei40gHJvIH4CQ&ved=0CDEQuwUwAA#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20210414163539 }} Ten Speed Press. p. 4. {{ISBN|978-0-89815-994-3}}.</ref>

蛭石總氮含量的增加，可用氮磷的增加以及污泥和土壤中重金屬的去除量增加。在許多研究中已經觀察到重金屬的生物利用度的降低。<ref>{{Cite journal|title = Comparative Study on Physical and Chemical Characteristics of Sludge Vermicomposted by Eisenia Fetida|url = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1878029612005968|journal = Procedia Environmental Sciences|date = 2012-01-01|pages = 418–423|volume = 16|series = The Seventh International Conference on Waste Management and Technology (ICWMT 7)|doi = 10.1016/j.proenv.2012.10.058|first = Fei|last = Liu|first2 = Pengfei|last2 = Zhu|first3 = Jianping|last3 = Xue}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title = Heavy metal and nutrient changes during vermicomposting animal manure spiked with mushroom residues|journal = Waste Management (New York, N.Y.)|date = 2014-11-01|issn = 1879-2456|pmid = 25128918|pages = 1977–1983|volume = 34|issue = 11|doi = 10.1016/j.wasman.2014.07.013|first = Xiuchao|last = Song|first2 = Manqiang|last2 = Liu|first3 = Di|last3 = Wu|first4 = Lin|last4 = Qi|first5 = Chenglong|last5 = Ye|first6 = Jiaguo|last6 = Jiao|first7 = Feng|last7 = Hu}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title = Microbial biodegradation of waste materials for nutrients enrichment and heavy metals removal: An integrated composting-vermicomposting process|url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/262194513_Microbial_biodegradation_of_waste_materials_for_nutrients_enrichment_and_heavy_metals_removal_An_integrated_composting-vermicomposting_process|journal = International Biodeterioration & Biodegradation|pages = 41–48|volume = 92|doi = 10.1016/j.ibiod.2014.04.011|first = Seyede Maryam|last = Kharrazi|first2 = Habibollah|last2 = Younesi|first3 = Javad|last3 = Abedini-Torghabeh|access-date = 2017-10-02|archive-date = 2019-07-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190724233026/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/262194513_Microbial_biodegradation_of_waste_materials_for_nutrients_enrichment_and_heavy_metals_removal_An_integrated_composting-vermicomposting_process|dead-url = no}}</ref>

==優點==
===土壤===
* 改善其物理結構。
* 豐富的土壤與微生物。
* 吸引深挖洞蚯蚓已經存在於土壤。
* 提高持水能力。

===植物生長===
* 增強發芽，植物生長和作物產量。
* 提高根系生長和結構。
* 豐富的土壤與微生物。

===經濟===
* 轉換減少了廢料堆填區。
* 低資本投資和相對簡單的技術使蚯蚓分解處理實際的欠發達的農業區。

===環境===
* 大型系統通常使用溫度控制，機械化收割，但其他設備相對簡單。
* 生產減少溫室氣體排放，如甲烷和一氧化氮（用垃圾填埋場或焚燒時不堆肥或通過甲烷收穫）。

== 使用 ==
[[File:Wormbin.bedding.jpg|thumb]]
=== 土壤調理劑 ===
蚯蚓可以直接混入土壤。

由於含有豐富的水分和有機酸的可能性，黑色的廢液或滲濾液可能會因為富含水分的食物而被排入一些蚯蚓體系的底部。 對植物有毒。

這些肥料的pH，營養和微生物含量因供應給蠕蟲的輸入而異。 可以將粉碎的石灰石或碳酸鈣加入到體系中以提高pH。
{{-}}

== 操作和維護 ==
=== 氣味 ===
關閉時，維護良好的垃圾桶無臭；打開時應該有一點點氣味 如果有氣味，那就是泥土。<ref>Appelhof, p. 113</ref>蚯蚓需要保持一定的流動空氣。<ref>Appelhof, p. 92</ref>氧氣可以由垃圾箱中的氣孔提供，偶爾攪拌垃圾桶內容物，如果它們變得太深或太潮濕，則可以取出一些垃圾桶內容物。如果分解從添加到垃圾桶中的過量濕原料或者食物廢物層變得過深而變得厭氧，則垃圾箱將開始會產生[[氨|氨]]氣。

=== 水分 ===
如果分解成為厭氧菌，為了恢復健康狀況，防止蚯蚓死亡，必須除去臭味多餘的廢水，並將垃圾箱恢復到正常的水分。要做到這一點，首先要減少高含水量的食物添加劑，其次，加入新鮮的，乾燥的鋪墊，如切碎的報紙到你的箱子裡，混合好。

=== 害蟲物種 ===
害蟲如囓齒動物和蒼蠅被某些材料和氣味吸引，通常來自大量的廚房垃圾，特別是肉類。消除使用肉類或乳製品害蟲的可能性。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://oacc.info/DOCs/Vermiculture_FarmersManual_gm.pdf |title=Manual of On-Farm Vermicomposting and Vermiculture |accessdate=2009-12-10 |page=8 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091122210204/http://www.oacc.info/DOCs/Vermiculture_FarmersManual_gm.pdf |archivedate=2009-11-22 |df= }}</ref>

掠奪性螞蟻在非洲國家可能是一個問題。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=DAVID WATAKO, KOSLENGAR MOUGABE, and THOMAS HEATH|first=|year=April 2016|title=Tiger worm toilets: lessons learned from constructing household vermicomposting toilets in Liberia|url=|journal=Waterlines|volume=35| issue =  2|pages=136–147|via=}}</ref>

在溫暖的天氣中，如果果蔬和蔬菜廢物沒有被鋪墊覆蓋，水果和醋會在箱子中發酵。通過至少{{convert|5|cm|in}}的鋪墊完全覆蓋廢物可以避免這個問題。保持正確的pH（接近中性）和水箱內的水分（恰好足夠的水，擠壓的鋪墊滴下幾滴）可以幫助避免這些害蟲。

=== 蚯蚓逃避 ===
蚯蚓通常停留在垃圾箱中，可能會在首次引入時嘗試離開垃圾桶，常常發生在室外濕度高時經常暴雨。首次引入蚯蚓時，維護蟲體中的足夠條件並將其放在垃圾桶上，應該能夠消除這個問題。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.coldclimategarden.com/en/can-you-do-vermicomposting-in-an-apartment/ |title=Can you do vermicomposting in an apartment? |access-date=2017-10-02 |archive-date=2016-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005065728/http://www.coldclimategarden.com/en/can-you-do-vermicomposting-in-an-apartment/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 營養水平 ===
商業蛭石試驗，並可修改其產品，以產生一致的質量和結果。 由於小規模和家庭系統使用各種各樣的原料混合物，所以造成的粉塵的氮，鉀和磷含量也將不一致。 在將蚯蚓或茶葉應用於花園之前，NPK測試可能是有幫助的。

